Mission Orders

Nagas are guarding the north Gallery on the second floor of the Temple.

Hunt {@LinkCreature:42#220#naga zealots}, {@LinkCreature:42#230#dagonite templars}, {@LinkCreature:42#320#naga soldiers}, {@LinkCreature:42#1010#mekonari zealots}, and {@LinkCreature:42#1020#mekonari bloodletters}.

Report to Coordinator Glasrinne when mission is complete.
You’ve earned the thanks of the federation.
It looks like you haven’t completed your mission yet.
